---
---

<div id="quick-reference-popup" class="quick-reference-popup" style="display: none;">
  <div class="quick-reference-overlay"></div>
  <div class="quick-reference-content">
    <div class="quick-reference-header">
      <h2 class="quick-reference-title">📚 Referência Rápida</h2>
      <button id="close-quick-reference" class="close-quick-reference" type="button" aria-label="Fechar">✕</button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="quick-reference-body">
      <div class="reference-grid">
        <!-- Tabela de Dificuldades (ND 1-45) -->
        <div class="reference-card">
          <h3 class="reference-title">🎯 Tabela de Dificuldades (ND 1-45)</h3>
          <div class="reference-content">
            <table class="reference-table nd-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>ND</th>
                  <th>Dificuldade</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>1-3</td><td>Trivial</td></tr>
                <tr><td>4-6</td><td>Muito Fácil</td></tr>
                <tr><td>7-9</td><td>Fácil</td></tr>
                <tr><td>10-12</td><td>Médio-Fácil</td></tr>
                <tr><td>13-18</td><td>Médio</td></tr>
                <tr><td>19-24</td><td>Difícil</td></tr>
                <tr><td>25-30</td><td>Muito Difícil</td></tr>
                <tr><td>31-36</td><td>Quase Impossível</td></tr>
                <tr><td>37-42</td><td>Extremamente Difícil</td></tr>
                <tr><td>43-45</td><td>Divino</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Ações de Combate (colapsáveis) -->
        <div class="reference-card accordion-card">
          <h3 class="reference-title">⚔️ Ações de Combate</h3>
          <div class="reference-content">
            <details class="ref-accordion-item">
              <summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Ação padrão</strong></summary>
              <p class="ref-accordion-detail">No seu turno você dispõe de uma ação padrão: atacar, usar uma habilidade que exija ação padrão, interagir com objeto relevante, etc., conforme as regras do livro.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item">
              <summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Ação bônus</strong></summary>
              <p class="ref-accordion-detail">Só ocorre quando uma habilidade ou efeito concede explicitamente uma ação bônus adicional naquele turno; não é um recurso genérico extra.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item">
              <summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Movimento</strong></summary>
              <p class="ref-accordion-detail">Deslocamento em metros até o valor de Movimento no turno, salvo reduções por condições, carga ou outras regras aplicáveis.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item">
              <summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Esquiva</strong></summary>
              <p class="ref-accordion-detail">Reação de defesa. Declare-a na janela indicada pelo livro (antes da rolagem de ataque contra você). A resolução usa Esquiva e Defesa passiva conforme a regra da mesa.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item">
              <summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Bloqueio</strong></summary>
              <p class="ref-accordion-detail">Reação. Declare antes de saber se o ataque acertou. Se o golpe acertar, você aplica sua Resistência a dano físico para reduzir o dano recebido.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Condições (colapsáveis) -->
        <div class="reference-card accordion-card">
          <h3 class="reference-title">⚡ Condições</h3>
          <div class="reference-content">
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Machucado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Vida &lt; 50%. Movimento reduzido pela metade.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Morrendo</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Vida = 0. Movimento zerado. Testes de salvamento.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Insano</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Sanidade &lt; 50%. Afeta testes sociais e mentais.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Sobrecarregado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Peso &gt; máximo. Movimento reduzido pela metade.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Atordoado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Incapacitado, não pode se mover ou agir.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Cego/Surdo</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Desvantagem em testes que dependem do sentido.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Enfeitiçado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Não pode atacar o enfeitiçador.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Envenenado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Dano periódico. Desvantagem até ser curado.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Queimado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Dano contínuo. Desvantagem até extinguir.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Assustado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Desvantagem enquanto a fonte do medo estiver visível.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Paralisado/Inconsciente</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Incapacitado. Não pode agir.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Agarrado/Restrito</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Movimento zerado.</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Invisível/Escondido</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Vantagem em ataques surpresa.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cálculos Rápidos (colapsáveis) -->
        <div class="reference-card accordion-card">
          <h3 class="reference-title">🧮 Cálculos Rápidos</h3>
          <div class="reference-content">
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Modificador de Atributo</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">(Valor - 10) ÷ 2 (arredondado para baixo)</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Vida Máxima</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Brutalidade + Compleição + bônus de nível + extra</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Mana Máxima</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Sobrenatural × 2 + bônus de nível + extra</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Sanidade Máxima</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Mente × 2 + bônus de nível + extra</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Resistência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">MOD Compleição + MOD Brutalidade ÷ 2</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Movimento</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Destreza ÷ 2 (em metros) + extra</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Defesa passiva</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">8 + modificador de Destreza + modificador de Compleição</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sequências (colapsáveis) -->
        <div class="reference-card accordion-card">
          <h3 class="reference-title">🔮 Sequências</h3>
          <div class="reference-content">
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>9ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 1-2</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>8ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 3-4</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>7ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 5-6</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>6ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 7-8</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>5ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 9-10</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>4ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 11-12</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>3ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 13-14</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>2ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 15-16</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>1ª Sequência</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">Níveis 17-20</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Treinamentos (colapsáveis) -->
        <div class="reference-card accordion-card">
          <h3 class="reference-title">📖 Bônus de Treinamento</h3>
          <div class="reference-content">
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Nenhum</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">+0</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Básico</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">+2</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Médio</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">+4</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Avançado</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">+6</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Expert</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">+8</p></details>
            <details class="ref-accordion-item"><summary class="ref-accordion-summary"><strong>Aterrorizante</strong></summary><p class="ref-accordion-detail">+10</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="module">
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const popup = document.getElementById('quick-reference-popup');
    const overlay = popup?.querySelector('.quick-reference-overlay');
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById('close-quick-reference');
    const openBtn = document.getElementById('open-quick-reference');

    function openPopup() {
      if (popup) {
        popup.style.display = 'flex';
        document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
      }
    }

    function closePopup() {
      if (popup) {
        popup.style.display = 'none';
        document.body.style.overflow = '';
      }
    }

    if (openBtn) {
      openBtn.addEventListener('click', openPopup);
    }

    if (closeBtn) {
      closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closePopup);
    }

    if (overlay) {
      overlay.addEventListener('click', closePopup);
    }

    // Fechar com ESC
    document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
      if (e.key === 'Escape' && popup && popup.style.display === 'flex') {
        closePopup();
      }
    });

    // Exportar função para uso externo
    window.openQuickReference = openPopup;
    window.closeQuickReference = closePopup;
  });
</script>

<style>
  .quick-reference-popup {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 10001;
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .quick-reference-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .quick-reference-content {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-primary);
    border-radius: 16px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    max-height: 90vh;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 0 60px rgba(139, 76, 141, 0.3);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .quick-reference-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
    border-radius: 14px 14px 0 0;
  }

  .quick-reference-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-accent);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .close-quick-reference {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .close-quick-reference:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    background: rgba(139, 76, 141, 0.2);
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .quick-reference-body {
    padding: 2rem;
    overflow-y: auto;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .reference-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reference-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .reference-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139, 76, 141, 0.2);
  }

  .reference-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--color-text-accent);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .reference-content {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .reference-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .reference-table th,
  .reference-table td {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .reference-table th {
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    color: var(--color-text-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .reference-table tr:hover {
    background: rgba(139, 76, 141, 0.05);
  }

  .ref-accordion-item {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ref-accordion-summary {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .ref-accordion-summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .ref-accordion-summary::before {
    content: '▶';
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .ref-accordion-item[open] .ref-accordion-summary::before {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .ref-accordion-summary strong {
    color: var(--color-text-accent);
  }

  .ref-accordion-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .ref-accordion-detail {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem 0.75rem 2rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quick-reference-popup {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .quick-reference-content {
      max-height: 95vh;
    }

    .quick-reference-header {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .quick-reference-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .quick-reference-body {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .reference-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

